thread.title: Alexander Andrew St.Helier-Bourke
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by Alexander Andrew St.Helier-Bourke

author: Alexander Andrew St.Helier-Bourke
title: Alexander Andrew St.Helier-Bourke
text:
Over the years I have used Ace on several occasions, and can highly recommend them.
There staff are always cheerful and helpful.
The cars always exceed my expectations for trouble free motoring.
I have no hesitation in recommending Ace for great cars at excellent prices.
